snippet.title: Fallen Overlord | A new web game
snippet.description:
Dare to challenge one of the hardest games ever?! Beat the 99 floors and face the king on the 100th floor!

The game includes a leaderboard for you to share your score with the whole world!

Game link: https://codya.co/fallen-overlord
Alternative link: https://codya.itch.io/fallen-overlord

If you have any feedback, please leave a comment below.
